claim: The United Kingdom borders six bodies of water.
premise_source_doc_sentence: The six bodies were and remain : The United Synagogue of America , The Rabbinical Assembly  (  Conservative  )  ; The Union of Orthodox Jewish Congregations , The Rabbinical Council of America  (  Orthodox  )  ; The Union of American Hebrew Congregations , The Central Conference of American Rabbis  (  Reform  )  .
